55 Enchanter -- Tallon Zek <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/uabyena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Abyena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#330000>(3/6/02 12:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=74.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: charm soloing</span><hr size=1> Ah honestly I've done some with velk spiders, FG shrooms, and a little bit with mobs in HS. Well that gave xp anyway. A little risky, but beats all the boring tash, buff, slow, buff of normal group xping. ^  ^ <br>
