Ethereal, 7th Hammer</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ureisswolff.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Reiss Wolff</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#330000>(4/5/02 4:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=74.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: charm soloing</span><hr size=1> I do it sometimes in DL or Karnors...<br>
