<br>
The only real dangers in the zone at 60 are the Shimmering Rockfiends, which make awe-inspiring pets should you chose to charm them, but which require extra caution to handle charm breaks. <p><font size="-1" face="Arial,Hevetica,Sans-Serif"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52833">My Magelo Profile</a> |
